                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930109-39-defend388 t17930109-39-punish215"></join>
               Publickly Whipped
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
